Package: usaspending
Title: Interface to USAspending.gov API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("James Joseph", "Balamuta", , "james.balamuta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive interface to the USAspending.gov API, 
    allowing users to access federal spending data including agency budgets, 
    awards, recipients, and more. The package implements the complete v2 API
    with consistent return formats and error handling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
